            열린옷장에 직접문의하세요 (02-6929-1020)
          </div>
          <div class="mr-2 h3 box-link-arrow"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
    <a class="box-link" href="<%= $urls->{event_seoul} %>">
      <div class="card box-link-event">
        <div class="card-body pt-5 pb-5 pl-3 ">
          <div class="box-link-title">
            <span><span class="span1">서울시 </span><span class="span2">정장 무료대여 바로가기</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="mr-2 h3 box-link-arrow"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
    <a class="box-link" href="<%= $urls->{event_gyeonggi} %>">
      <div class="card box-link-event">
        <div class="card-body pt-5 pb-5 pl-3 ">
          <div class="box-link-title">
            <span><span class="span1">경기 </span><span class="span2">정장 무료대여 정보 보기</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="mr-2 h3 box-link-arrow"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
